divs: Sighting Detailsit was blue green size of a small car. it came straight down out of the clouds at a extreme speed with no light on impact or sound. i was on my way back to portage from dells on the interstate and it lit up a 20 mile area before i lost site just off the ground by cascade. whatever it was it was not free falling. it was as if it was shot straight at the ground It blew through the cloud cover and hit the ground in under 5 seconds.scared the 3 of us! i seen a state trooper when i got off on hyw 33 headed that way. then when i got home you could here jets VERY low flying over portage?
Summary: blue green light shot at ground
